                <img src="images/about/cafe-owner.jpeg" alt="★M'Café Founder">
            </div>
            <div class="about-text">
                <h3>Our Beginning</h3>
                <p>★M'Café began in 2020 with a simple idea: to create a space where quality coffee and freshly baked goods could bring people together. Our founder, Mmoloki Mooketsi, has always been passionate about both coffee and baking, honing his skills during his travels around the world.</p>
                <p>After returning to Botswana, Mmoloki noticed that while there were coffee shops and bakeries, few places combined exceptional versions of both. Thus, ★M'Café was born—a place where neither coffee nor pastries take a back seat.</p>
                <p>The star in our name represents our commitment to excellence in everything we serve, while the "M" stands for both Mmoloki and "Mmogo," the Setswana word for "together"—because we believe food and drink are best enjoyed in good company.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mission-section">
        <div class="mission-content">
