            <ul class="mission-list">
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Serve exceptional coffee using ethically sourced beans</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Create fresh, handcrafted pastries and baked goods daily</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Provide a warm, welcoming space for our community</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Support local producers and sustainable practices</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Celebrate Botswana's growing coffee culture</li>
